* Todd Gurley, NFL running back, 3x Pro Bowl selection and 2x First-team All-Pro
* Brian Hargrove, television writer/producer
* Montrezl Harrell, NBA player for the Philadelphia 76ers
* Janice Bryant Howroyd, first African American woman to build and own a billion dollar company
* Ben Jones, politician, actor
* Joshua Lawrence (1778–1843), influential Baptist minister in the early 19th century
* Derrick Lewis, professional basketball player
* Tyquan Lewis, NFL defensive lineman
* Jim Phillips Sr., North Carolina state senator
* General Hugh Shelton, former chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff
* Hubert Simmons, Negro league baseball player for the Baltimore Elite Giants
* Joseph K. Spiers, U.S. Air Force general
