==Sister cities==
Winston-Salem&#x27;s sister cities are:
* Buchanan, Liberia
* Freeport, Bahamas
* Kumasi, Ghana
* Nassau, Bahamas
* Ungheni, Moldova
* Yangpu (Shanghai), China

